caption:
Kylian Mbappé is currently the top scorer in La Liga in his debut season — what a comeback after everything he’s been through! 🤯⚽

No player has scored more league goals than Mbappé across Europe’s top five leagues this season. 🔝

After a difficult start marked by criticism and uncertainty, Mbappé has truly risen to the occasion. He’s stepped up for Real Madrid, consistently delivering goals even when the team hasn’t been at its best. His resilience, determination, and world-class talent are shining on the biggest stage. 👏

Now, he’s on the verge of winning both the Pichichi Trophy and the European Golden Boot — an incredible achievement in his first season in Spain.

Kylian Mbappe in La Liga this season:
🏟️ Games: 32
🚀 Goals: 28
🎯 Assists: 3
